      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for those. they're a good start. could you expand more on the national security aspect? like, specifically how supporters argue that an unsecured border isn't just about illegal work, but a genuine threat to the sovereign integrity of the state? i want my students to be able to argue the philosophical necessity of borders, not just the economic stuff.",
